title: Obama: U.S. credibility on the line with nuclear deal - CNN Video
text:
Fareed Zakaria, GPS | Source: CNN Added on 1833 GMT (0133 HKT) August 9, 2015 President Barack Obama says the United States' role in global politics could be affected by whether or not Congress approves the Iran nuclear deal.
Barack Obama: U.S. credibility on the line in Iran nuclear deal By Eric Bradner, CNN President Barack Obama says the United States' credibility -- beyond just the specifics of the negotiations and his tenure in the White House -- is on the line as Congress votes on the Iran nuclear deal.
More from World
